snippet.title: KLETKA - ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
Link to the game in the pinned comment!

About the game:
KLETKA is a co-op horror game about going down in an elevator that is trying to eat you. Feed the elevator, explore deadly floors and descend deeper.

We are pleased to announce our new project created in co-authorship with ln404!

Music Author: @dansmashphoto

#KLETKA #ln404 #Gaming #Trailer
